WITH 

source AS (
    SELECT * FROM "mage_db"."public"."real_estate_data"
),

geolocation AS (
    SELECT
        town AS geolocation_town,
        latitude,
        longitude,
        region
    FROM "mage_db"."public_public"."pt"  -- Join the geolocation seed (assuming it's named `pt`)
),

renamed AS (
    SELECT
        re.unique_id,
        re.price,
        re.district,
        re.city,
        re.town,
        re._type,
        re.energy_certificate,
        re.gross_area,
        re.total_area,
        re.parking,
        re.has_parking,
        re._floor,
        re.construction_year,
        re.energy_efficiency_level,
        re.publish_date,
        re.garage,
        re.elevator,
        re.electric_cars_charging,
        re.total_rooms,
        re.number_of_bedrooms,
        re.number_of_w_c,
        re.conservation_status,
        re.living_area,
        re.lot_size,
        re.built_area,
        re.number_of_bathrooms,
        re.push_date,
        geo.latitude,  -- Add latitude
        geo.longitude, -- Add longitude
        geo.region      -- Add region
    FROM source re
    LEFT JOIN geolocation geo
    ON LOWER(re.town) = LOWER(geo.geolocation_town)  -- Match towns (case-insensitive)
)

SELECT * FROM renamed
